Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
It's unfortunate that you were unable to attend our recent Gifted & Talented and Scholarship Information Evening.
For your information, attached is a copy of Dr Oslington's presentation and further information on our G&T and scholarship program..
If you have any further queries, our would like to take the opportunity to discuss your child's learning potential, please feel free to contact any of our Enrolments staff on 9286 9500.
Thank you again for your attendance and I look forward to the opportunity to welcome you and your family next time to St Andrew's Cathedral School.
Regards
Bruce Perry Registrar/Mathematics Teacher
phone 02 92869507 email BPerry@sacs.nsw.edu.au
